.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-FEE-BASE-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-fee-base-stddev \- FEAT-2748 stddev of fee_base across peers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-fee-base-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the standard deviation of fee_base_msat across peer channels (FEAT-2748).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_base_stddev_msat_peer\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
